<i>adverb</i>: 하나하나 [하나하나], 일일이 [일리리] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>하나하나 [하나하나]</dt><br>
<dd>1. one at a time; separately</dd><br>
<dd>하나씩 하나씩.</dd><br>
<dd>One by one.</dd><br>
<dd>2. singly; individually; one by one</dd><br>
<dd>한 사람씩 한 사람씩.</dd><br>
<dd>One person by one person.</dd><br>
<dd>3. in full; fully</dd><br>
<dd>하나씩 자세하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In detail, one by one.</dd><br>
<dd>4. in everything; in every case</dd><br>
<dd>여러 가지 조건에 그때그때마다.</dd><br>
<dd>Every time, with a lot of conditions, excuses, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>일일이 [일리리]</dt><br>
<dd>1. one at a time; separately</dd><br>
<dd>하나씩 하나씩.</dd><br>
<dd>One by one.</dd><br>
<dd>2. singly; individually; one by one</dd><br>
<dd>한 사람씩 한 사람씩.</dd><br>
<dd>One person by one person.</dd><br>
<dd>3. in full; fully</dd><br>
<dd>하나씩 자세하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In detail, one by one.</dd><br>
<dd>4. in everything; in every case</dd><br>
<dd>여러 가지 조건에 그때그때마다.</dd><br>
<dd>Every time, with a lot of conditions, excuses, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>